Events
Here at Dogwood Lakes we offer many forms of entertainment. Our unique golf course is just the best part of our venue. We host a comedy night approximately every 3 months, giving our locals a great laugh with comedians from all over.  We hold exceptional tournaments, with great food and prizes. Dogwood lakes is also a very important vital resource to the community, as we host several fundraisers, raise money for great scholarships, and also donate to the local womens and youth needs by raising funds every October with our annual witch ride. Our annual New Years Bash is the biggest around giving our local community a fantastic option to bring in the new year. Dogwood Lakes is very Proud of all our community involvement!Dogwood Lakes is also a great option to rent as a venue, you will need to book in advance as we fill our dates very quickly. We can seat 100-120 ppl comfortably, you may have your events catered or we can also provide decorating and catering services for a fee.
